ancellations and far longer journey times.Crowds built up at major Paris stations such as Montparnasse, where trains to and from nearby towns such as Tours and Le Mans were all cancelled.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1891, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.86620167044505e-23, \"text\": \"GV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volt\"}, {\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ouigo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ouigo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ouigo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ouigo\"}, {\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9666987439391984e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2053, \"end\": 2065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_Montparnasse\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.963663562686201e-12, \"text\": \"Montparnasse\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_Montparnasse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_Montparnasse\"}, {\"begin\": 2123, \"end\": 2130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Mans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.323544842994782e-17, \"text\": \"Le Mans\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Mans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Mans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"conventional lines\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"cancellations\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"far longer journey times\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"Crowds\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"near